    "This approach can optimize traffic flow in traffic management by penalizing actions or behaviors that cause congestion or delays.",
    "Our traffic control system uses negative rewards to disincentivize actions like abrupt lane changes or excessive speeding, thereby encouraging smoother and more efficient traffic patterns.",
    "By applying these penalties, the system can gradually refine its strategies to minimize traffic jams and improve overall flow.",
